# Student Info Viewer

## Description
A simple web-based student information viewer. Users can search for student names, view IDs, courses, and year levels. Built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  

## Features
- View student information in a table  
- Search/filter students by name  

## Usage
1. Download or clone the repository  
2. Type a name in the search box to filter students  

